## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
```bash
# 1. Run migration
php artisan migrate

# 2. Seed eselon tarif
php artisan db:seed --class=RefIuranEselonSeeder

# 3. Generate eselon mapping (dry-run dulu)
php artisan eselon:generate-mapping --dry-run

# 4. Generate mapping
php artisan eselon:generate-mapping

# 5. Verify mapping coverage
php artisan tinker --execute="
  \$total = \App\Models\Pegawai::aktif()->where('jenis_jabatan_id','1')->count();
  \$mapped = \App\Models\RefEselonMapping::count();
  echo \"Struktural: \$total, Mapped: \$mapped\";
"
```

### Manual / Browser Verification
- Buka **Laporan Iuran (Golongan)**: Pastikan kolom menampilkan nominal, bukan jumlah
- Toggle PNS/PPPK: Pastikan angka berubah sesuai filter
- Buka **Rincian Iuran**: Pilih OPD dari dropdown, verifikasi 2 tabel (eselon + golongan)
- Buka **Dashboard MARI**: Pastikan chart Top 10 OPD muncul di posisi yang benar
- Cross-check: Grand Total di Rincian Iuran (semua OPD) = Total Iuran di Dashboard

